<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Movie Booking</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .movie-title {
      color: #333;
    }
    .movie-poster {
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
    .form-group label {
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .form-control {
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background-color: #007bff;
      border-color: #007bff;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
      border-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="text-center movie-title mb-4">Movie Booking</h1>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <img src="movie4.png" alt="Movie Poster">
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h2 class="movie-title">HER</h2>
        <p>
            
"Her" is a science fiction romance film directed by Spike Jonze. Set in a near-future Los Angeles, the story follows Theodore Twombly (played by Joaquin Phoenix), a lonely and introverted man who works as a professional writer of personal letters for others. Theodore becomes intrigued by a new artificially intelligent operating system named Samantha (voiced by Scarlett Johansson), which is designed to adapt and evolve like a human.</p>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="date">Select Date:</label>
          <input type="date" id="date" class="form-control">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="tickets">Number of Tickets:</label>
          <input type="number" id="tickets" class="form-control" min="1" value="1">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="seating">Select Seating Area:</label>
          <select id="seating" class="form-control">
            <option value="gold">Gold Area</option>
            <option value="silver">Silver Area</option>
            <option value="bronze">Bronze Area</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <button class="btn btn-primary">Book Now</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
